editionStmt.p: The transcription of the glosses was made by Nike Stam and formed the basis of her thesis ‘A Typology of Code-Switching in the Commentary to the Félire Óengusso', (University of Utrecht, 2017), in which the bilingual glosses were translated and analysed.
